text: Armand Walter (5 April 1908 - 11 July 1995) was a French gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:1995 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Haut-Rhin
